    "en": {
      "title": "15 murders in three months",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior police officer said that 15 murders have taken place in Galle district in the three months from June 1st to August 31st this year.",
        "It is to be noted that 12 of these murders involved shootings, seven were in Ambalangoda area and the other three were murders with sharp weapons."
